{"tid":2386801,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"因為GME事件，ARK已經連續三日無錢流入","createTime":"2021-01-29T21:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T05:25:18.000Z","uid":295230,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1e449eb2272b34bf92e1d2dac50aa7b22647f818","tid":2386801,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T21:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>GameStop Drama Is So Big That It&rsquo;s Overshadowing Cathie Wood</strong><br />\n<br />\n(Bloomberg) -- With all Wall Street eyes on GameStop Corp., a months-long obsession with Cathie Wood&rsquo;s Ark Investment Management is finally showing signs of easing.<br />\n<br />\nUntil the video game retailer stole the headlines, Ark was the hottest thing in investment, luring billions in new money amid the dash to thematic exchange-traded funds. <strong><span class=\"red\">Now its main ETF has gone without an inflow for three days for the first time since October -- and could post a weekly outflow for the first time since Covid struck.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nThe rapid change underscores how WallStreetBets and its army of day traders have disrupted the normal order of business across the financial world<strong><span class=\"red\"></span></strong>. So far at least, they&rsquo;re more interested in single names like GameStop and AMC Entertainment Holdings Inc. than ETFs. The 10% gain year-to-date for the firm&rsquo;s flagship Ark Innovation ETF (ARKK) isn&rsquo;t nearly as eye-popping as GameStop&rsquo;s leap of more than 1,281% as of 2:30 p.m. in New York.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The speculative mania in &lsquo;Reddit stocks&rsquo; has simply overshadowed Ark Invest and pretty much everything else in the markets,&rdquo; said Nate Geraci, president of the ETF Store, an investment advisory firm. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s a fascinating dichotomy right now with investors pumping money into companies of the past versus companies of the future.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nARKK has lost more than $100 million in the past three days, according to data compiled by Bloomberg. While that&rsquo;s a drop in the bucket for the $23 billion fund, it&rsquo;s a stark shift from the 19 straight days of inflows prior, including its best day on record Jan. 8 with $626 million added. At the same time, its $11 billion Ark Genomic Revolution ETF (ARKG) also lost about $100 million in the past two days."},{"pid":"acefcaf0ca26e46c64944f7e0fc9230fbc2c84e7","tid":2386801,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T21:54:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ark-mania-finally-fading-gamestop-145324678.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fark-mania-finally-fading-gamestop-145324678.html&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d57eaf14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ark-mania-finally-fading-gamestop-145324678.html</a>"},{"pid":"8aad6f657ff25a2a1a72a35b04854dde2017f893","tid":2386801,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTim